## TENSION WORTH RESOLVING

The product app's funnel is built around **opened / clicked**, but the landing
brief bans those stats as bot-inflated. Both can be right ‚Äî internal
diagnostics vs external claims ‚Äî but decide it deliberately rather than by
accident.

